* copy bash/* to $HOME
* copy vim/* to $HOME
* copy bin to $HOME/tools
* copy scripts to $HOME/tools

Under Windows:
* shutdown.py for shutdowning computer in/at special time

Other:
* old/* for old scripts which have been replaced

